License: Artistic/GPL
Group: Applications/CPAN
URL: http://search.cpan.org/dist/Cache-Memcached/

Source: http://search.cpan.org/CPAN/authors/id/D/DO/DORMANDO/Cache-Memcached-%{version}.tar.gz
